  "body": "  The number of members of Eastonboro YMCA as a function of years since 2000, is given by the formula . Find the average rate of change in the Y's memberships between 2003 and 2011. Include units in your answer. Does it seem likely that this average rate of change would always be the same? Why or why not?   "
